# === Ziggy Racer — .gitignore ===

# --- recordings/: ignore ALL of it (multi-GB telemetry logs, survey sweeps, learned
#     online state, dev datasets) EXCEPT the small derived model artifacts that make the
#     pipeline inspectable and let the controller run. ---
recordings/*
!recordings/refline_plan.npz
!recordings/surface_cap.npz
!recordings/surface_sheet.npz
!recordings/bank_map.npz
!recordings/load_map.npz
!recordings/sections.json
!recordings/vehicle_spec.json

# --- Runtime logs & captured artifacts ---
*.log
follower_std*.log
follower_std*.txt
wd_fail_*.log
survey.log
train_*.log
*.png
scratchpad/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.DS_Store

# --- Local machine cruft ---
*.bak
*.orig

# keep curated images used by the docs/README
!docs/media/*.png
!docs/media/*.jpg

# --- organized 07-20 ---
logs/
recordings/archive_logs/
recordings/archive_data/
recordings/snapshots/
